# ---------------- stage 2: the dimension gate for H^0(omega_C~) ----------------
# eta_j = t^j * (g / F_u) * pi^* omega0,  g = sum_i a_i(x,y) u^i.
# Regularity per branch:  v(g-expansion) >= j*v(t) ... rearranged:
